message.body: Hey! umm, not much is up! i'm upstate right now, i'm coming home tonight! the end of the year is actually really stressful and work-filled!! how are you?? what's up? i saw that you were in grease at your school! how was that??

Oh awesome! Yeah I know, I have two papers due next week and there are only 10 days left of the school year...wtf. I'm doing well, and grease was a lot of fun! It really helped take my mind off of school. Are you excited for smith?? Also we all have to hang out this summer or during regents week!

Yeah i have final papers/projects for all my classes due in the next two weeks!! it's soo dumb!! that's awesome!! yeah, i'm really excited about Simth!! where are you going? chicago? (sorry i forgot!) yeah, i really want to see everyone at some point this summer!!
Haha Ryan's going to Chicago. I'm going to emory in Atlanta Georgia! I'm pretty excited as well
I know lolol ABD told me! I don't know her at all tho, awks
Haha, yeah! well, it's a big school!! are you pumped to get some southern hospitality??
Lolol yeah! People are telling me that I'm crazy for going to the south because it's such a different culture but I'm actually really excited and not scared
